oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Willie Nelson at Star of Desert Arena
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Nelson, Willie, 1933-; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (blue and red on yellow) announcing an evening with Willie Nelson, singer, songwriter, actor, and author, at the Star of the Desert Arena at the Primm Valley Resort on January 24, 2009. Poster features a metal photoplate of Willie Nelson and is a limited edition of 50.
